  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个进程状态转换图，要体现现代操作系统的完整生命周期，包括挂起状态。起点是进程创建，终点是进程终止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "New",
        "Terminated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那基本状态除了New之外，应该有Ready、Running、Waiting这些经典状态对吧？另外挂起状态您说的是Suspended Ready和Suspended Wait两种？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "New",
        "Ready",
        "Running",
        "Waiting",
        "Suspended_Ready",
        "Suspended_Wait"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，挂起状态分两种：挂起就绪和挂起等待。另外调度器要区分清楚——准入调度器负责New到Ready，短期调度器负责Ready到Running，长期调度器管换入换出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "admission scheduler",
        "scheduler",
        "long-term scheduler",
        "New",
        "Ready",
        "Running"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程：New经过Admit进入Ready，然后Dispatch到Running。Running可以因为I/O等待进入Waiting，或者被Interrupt抢占回到Ready，还有Exit到Terminated。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "New",
        "Ready",
        "Running",
        "Waiting",
        "Terminated",
        "Admit",
        "Dispatch",
        "Interrupt",
        "Exit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Running到Waiting的转换要标注清楚是I/O或事件等待。还有，Waiting完成I/O后要能回到Ready。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Waiting",
        "Ready",
        "I/O or event wait",
        "I/O completed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在把挂起分支加上：Waiting可以被长期调度器Swap out到Suspended Wait，Suspended Wait在I/O完成后进入Suspended Ready。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Waiting",
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Suspended_Ready",
        "Swap out",
        "I/O completed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里有个细节——Suspended Wait的I/O完成和Waiting的I/O完成含义不同。前者只是I/O做完了但进程还在外存，后者是进程直接回到内存就绪队列。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Waiting",
        "I/O completed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，所以两者都用\"I/O completed\"标注，但去向不同：Waiting回Ready，Suspended Wait去Suspended Ready。那Suspended Ready怎么回到主流程？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Waiting",
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Suspended_Ready",
        "Ready",
        "I/O completed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Suspended Ready通过Swap in换入内存，回到Ready状态，这也是长期调度器的工作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Suspended_Ready",
        "Ready",
        "Swap in",
        "long-term scheduler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。现在检查下：Terminated要连回终止符，Running的抢占要明确标注preemption。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Terminated",
        "[*]",
        "Running",
        "Ready",
        "preemption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Running到Ready的Interrupt标注最好写成\"Interrupt (preemption)\"，这样更专业。还有New的入口转换要标注\"Process created\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Ready",
        "Interrupt",
        "preemption",
        "New",
        "[*]",
        "Process created"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正。另外Exit的标注我写成\"Exit (process completion)\"，和preemption的格式保持一致。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Running",
        "Terminated",
        "Exit",
        "process completion"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "很好。再确认一下长期调度器的两个操作：Swap out和Swap in都要标注清楚是它负责的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "long-term scheduler",
        "Swap out",
        "Swap in",
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Suspended_Ready",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加标注：Waiting到Suspended Wait是\"Swap out (long-term scheduler)\"，Suspended Ready到Ready是\"Swap in (long-term scheduler)\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Waiting",
        "Suspended_Wait",
        "Suspended_Ready",
        "Ready",
        "Swap out",
        "Swap in",
        "long-term scheduler"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Admit也要标注是admission scheduler，Dispatch标注scheduler就行，这是行业惯例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "New",
